name: Rebecca Ferguson - Embedding
description:
This is an embedding trained on 29 images of Swedish actress Rebecca Ferguson. Yeah, I know, I thought she was English, too. If the name doesn't ring a bell, she's the pretty lady in the last couple Mission Impossible movies, Hercules, Life and Doctor Sleep, among others.

Trained on SD1.5, but most output testing done with RinaMix2 (available on my profile). Also tested in several other checkpoints. See samples.

You may need to fiddle with the weights on some models, as a lot of the fancier illustration models sometimes need more coaxing to work well with some embeddings.

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description:
base version.

trained with a variable training rate of:

0.05:10, 0.02:20, 0.01:60, 0.005:200, 0.002:500, 0.001:3000, 0.0005

which overcooked the embedding, so training was resumed from step 500 at a lower training rate, and run until 15,000 steps.
